SLAKOTH lolls around for over twenty
hours every day. Because it moves so
little, it does not need much food. This POKMONs sole daily meal consists

SLAKOTHs heart beats just once a
minute. Whatever happens, it is
content to loaf around motionless. It is rare to see this POKMON in
motion.

by swimming in rivers.
